headline: 3 Reasons Investors Love Insulet (PODD)
summary: Insulet has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 18%. The stock now trades at $337, marking a 35.7% gain. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
